snippet.title: Dog kNOwSE Chapter 1 The Dame - Playthrough
snippet.description:
https://ledbetter-games.itch.io/dog-knowse
CW: Anthropomorphic Animal Violence - No animals were harmed in the making of Dog kNOwSE
-----
Dog kNOwSE began as a book in the concept library at the top of the ART&.. More gallery for the Playdate. This is the More part. 

The first chapter of this story was produced for Playjam 3 by Ledbetter Games and released for free on itch.io   https://ledbetter-games.itch.io/dog-knowse

There will be an announcement about the future of Dog in the coming weeks, but for now, enjoy a full playthrough of the Dog kNOwSE Chapter 1 storyline!
